x on cylinder iff

norm(x - (x@uax)*uax) == radius

ie

(x0 - (x0*u0 + x1*u1 + x2*u2)*u0)**2
+ (x1 - (x0*u0 + x1*u1 + x2*u2)*u1)**2
+ (x2 - (x0*u0 + x1*u1 + x2*u2)*u2)**2
== radius**2

x = e + t*d, solve for t

e + t*d - ((e + t*d)@uax)*uax is
e - (e@uax)*uax + t*(d - (d@uax)*uax)

call A, B
norm(A + t*B) == rad
solve
(a0 + t*b0)**2 + (a1 + t*b1)**2 + (a2 + t*b2)**2 == rad**2

(b0**2 + b1**2 + b2**2) t**2 +
2*(a0*b0 + a1*b1 + a2*b2) t +
(a0**2 + a1**2 + a2**2 - rad**2) == 0


